Name: Advantage Full Doc <55% LVR
ProductDetails: The Pepper Advantage suite is designed for customers who, due to restrictive credit criteria, are unable to meet the lending criteria of banks and mortgage insurers. With Pepper Advantage we assess each borrowers unique circumstances, rather than simply basing our decision on a credit score. Purchase or refinance of owner occupied and investment properties, also includes; unlimited debt consolidation, cash out for acceptable purposes and payment of ATO debts. Minor defaults up to $1,000 accepted. Unlimited defaults > $1,000, registered > 12 months (paid or unpaid). < 1 months mortgage arrears (within last 6 months). Discharged from bankruptcy (1 day accepted)
FeeDetails: Mortgage Risk Fee - 0.65% of amount advanced (0.50% MRF loading for loans >$1m). Title Protection Fee $400. Legal Fees from $440 plus disbursements. Estab Fee includes 1 standard valuation (Approx value $395)
RedrawDetails: MIn manual redraw $1000. Min online redraw $50
SplitDetails: Max 3 splits (inc 100% interest offset sub-account)
